<http://www.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/event/7802AKHHNGMHTPCQJCPSSQPTDLLHKQRDT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Consone Quartet";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Consone Quartet</h1><span><br/></span><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/files/9edbe421-eee0-4abf-a09c-e622265e1bb5.jpg\" /><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>London’s Consone Quartet returns to Vancouver with a selection of works by Beethoven, Haydn, Mendelssohn, and more. The first period instrument quartet to be selected as ‘BBC New Generation Artists’ (2022), Consone Quartet is fast making a name for themselves due to their sensitive and historically-informed approach to works of the Classical and early Romantic periods.
