  schema:description """
	<h1>Handel’s Messiah Vancouver</h1><span><br/></span><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/files/000aa2e6-ea52-46c0-9e8a-093f0c5d7a54.jpg\" /><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Early Music Vancouver and Vancouver Chamber Choir’s joint mounting of Handel’s indomitable Messiah returns to The Orpheum with a stellar lineup of soloists. At times reflective, joyful, solemn, and mysterious, this monumental work speaks to audiences across all worlds, bringing a fundamental message of hope. Alexander Weimann’s direction of this masterpiece is spell-binding.
