<http://www.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/event/7402ASMQTSCTVMHDSJKGJSMSBNJLMHLJR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Tafelmusik: Brilliant Baroque";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Tafelmusik: Brilliant Baroque</h1><span><br/></span><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/earlymusicvancouver/files/71156c3b-9eca-4c64-a67d-eea662c628c6.jpg\" /><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>World-renowned period orchestra Tafelmusik, known for their dynamic, engaging, and soulful performances, brings their latest programme to Vancouver, headed by British violinist and conductor Rachel Podger. Brilliant Baroque is a musical ‘tasting menu’ of Baroque gems for orchestra by Bach, Handel, and Purcell, perfect for newcomers and seasoned fans alike.
""";
